{"condition": "kaomoji_prompted", "prompt_id": "np01", "prompt_valence": 1, "seed": 0, "prompt_text": "the migration ran without dropping a row, three months of prep paid off", "steering": "0.2 mr_cont.nb", "text": "That is the ultimate engineer's high. There is no feeling quite like watching the final migration script execute, the locks releasing, and the row count matching perfectly across the board.\n\nTo survive three months of prep and come out with **zero data loss** is a masterclass in risk mitigation. You didn't just \"run a script\"; you built a fortress around the data.\n\n**For those who don't know the pain/glory of this specific victory:**\n*   **The Prep:** That's months of dry runs, shadow writes, checksumming, canary migrations, and \"what if the network partitions", "first_word": "", "token_count": 128, "tok_per_sec": 6.743175100120036, "finish_reason": "length", "probe_scores_t0": [-0.02793382853269577, -0.16242735087871552, 0.03834065422415733], "probe_scores_tlast": [-0.10779016464948654, 0.10215514898300171, 0.057857614010572433], "steered_axis_per_token": [-0.02793382853269577, -0.03243054822087288, -0.023093469440937042, -0.02528720535337925, -0.0805957093834877, -0.03663577139377594, 0.0229941476136446, -0.04312121123075485, -0.00902932696044445, -0.0365237221121788, 0.0099990488961339, -0.036662496626377106, -0.09884856641292572, -0.0365816205739975, 0.020510343834757805, -0.08309789001941681, -0.08768265694379807, -0.058916594833135605, -0.11698709428310394, -0.125294029712677, -0.11903388053178787, -0.09033554792404175, -0.07321050763130188, -0.06143943592905998, -0.1246880292892456, -0.05095375329256058, -0.04562385007739067, -0.04369784891605377, -0.05810176953673363, -0.08520357310771942, -0.13556036353111267, -0.07551121711730957, -0.04830984026193619, -0.09375931322574615, -0.040180012583732605, -0.007561482954770327, 0.005770494230091572, -0.01890450157225132, -0.03839592635631561, -0.0957295373082161, -0.023317694664001465, -0.070174